Insider Activity


Individual




Donald T. Grimes



Mr. Donald T. Grimes is SVP & Chief Financial & Operations Officer at Sally Beauty Holdings, Inc. and Co-Managing Director at mytheresa.com GmbH. Mr. Grimes was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer, COO & EVP by Neiman Marcus Group Ltd. LLC, Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Senior VP by Wolverine World Wide, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Keystone Automotive Operations, Inc., Vice President & Director-Beverage Finance by Brown-Forman Corp., a Principal by Coopers & Lybrand LLP, and EVP, Chief Operating & Financial Officer by Neiman Marcus Group, Inc. He received his MBA from Northwestern University.



